OL,3,CFormer student sentenced after bomb-
OL,4,Cmaking video found on phone
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man has been sentenced
OL,7,Fafter "detailed guide" on how to make
OL,8,Fa bomb was found on his phone.
OL,10,FAdam Mahmood was found guilty at
OL,11,FBirmingham Crown Court of possessing a
OL,12,Frecording likely to be useful to a
OL,13,Fperson committing or preparing an act
OL,14,Fof terrorism, after a week-long trial
OL,15,Fin September.
OL,17,FHe was sentenced to four years in a
OL,18,Fyoung offender institution.
