OL,6,FJudge Simon Drew KC remarked that an
OL,7,F"alarming display of medieval
OL,8,Fweaponry" was also found at the home
OL,9,Fof the former motor mechanics student,
OL,10,Fincluding knives, an axe and a
OL,11,Fcatapult.
OL,13,FMahmood claimed these items were
OL,14,Flinked to his interest in "Islamic
OL,15,Fhistory".
OL,17,FThe trial at Birmingham Crown Court
OL,18,Fwas told he had more than 27,000
OL,19,Ffollowers on TikTok and asked another
OL,20,Fuser to send him the instructional
OL,21,Fvideo via a messaging app.
