OL,6,FMahmood, who sat in the dock to be
OL,7,Fsentenced, was told by Judge Simon
OL,8,FDrew KC he will serve an extended
OL,9,Fperiod of three years on licence after
OL,10,Fhis custodial sentence expires "in
OL,11,Forder to protect the public in the
OL,12,Ffuture".
OL,14,FThe trial heard the video - which was
OL,15,Fobtained by Mahmood in October 2023 -
OL,16,Fprovided "a detailed guide" to
OL,17,Fproducing an explosive substance with
OL,18,Fa detonator and shrapnel to make a
OL,19,Fcomplete bomb.
