OL,6,FSentencing Mahmood, who is a former
OL,7,Fmotor mechanics student, the judge
OL,8,Fsaid: "You had terrorist motivations.
OL,9,FThat is clear from the items in your
OL,10,Fbedroom, the material on your phone
OL,11,Fand your evidence."
OL,13,FAlthough there was no evidence that
OL,14,FMahmood, of Platt Brook Way, Sheldon,
OL,15,FBirmingham, intended to use the bomb-
OL,16,Fmaking video for a specific terrorist
OL,17,Fact the judge said.
