OL,6,FHe noted the ball bearings found in
OL,7,Fhis bedroom suggested the defendant
OL,8,Fwas "at least contemplating assembling
OL,9,Fsuch a device".
OL,11,FThe judge added: "The presence of such
OL,12,Fan arsenal in the bedroom of an 18-
OL,13,Fyear-old was a clear warning sign.
OL,15,F"One that regrettably no responsible
OL,16,Fadult acted upon."
